Package ca.peterzhu.basestation.googlemaps

Provides all the classes to create Google Maps for the JSF frontend.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllBaseStationMap
    Contains a map with all the Base Station and works with the BaseStationSearch class to provide searching.
    BaseStationSearch
    Contains all the fields for searching for the AllBaseStationMap class.
    Geocode
    Provides geocoding service using the Google Maps services for Java.
    LocationDragMap
    Provides a draggable map for the new/edit base station page.

Package ca.peterzhu.basestation.googlemaps Description
